sections.heading: to 69-32-21 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1987, ch. 234, § 84 repealed 69-32-1 to 69-32-21 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 153, §§ 246 to 250, 255, 256, 258, 259, 261, and 263 to 265 and Laws 1975, ch. 63, § 1, relating to explosives for mines other than coal, effective July 1, 1987. For present comparable provisions,see69-8-1 to 69-8-15 NMSA 1978.
